@AdminService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5138

### Test AdminService trực tiếp
GET {{AdminService_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/test
Accept: application/json

### Thống kê người dùng (không cần token)
GET {{AdminService_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/users
Accept: application/json

### Dashboard admin (cần token admin)
GET {{AdminService_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json

### Test qua Gateway - Không cần token
GET https://localhost:7009/api-admin/dashboard/test
Accept: application/json

### Test qua Gateway - Thống kê người dùng
GET https://localhost:7009/api-admin/dashboard/users
Accept: application/json

### Test qua Gateway - Dashboard admin (cần token)
GET https://localhost:7009/api-admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json